peopleAlsoAsk.question: What makes a 1904 Indian Head penny valuable today?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet: The Indian Head penny, in particular, is valuable for a handful of reasons. First and foremost, the coin holds great historical significance. The coin played an important role in American history. After all, it went into production right before the start of the Civil War and it managed to withstand that battle.

peopleAlsoAsk.question: What is the error on the 1904 penny?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet: Re-punched date. This error is relatively rare among the 1904 pennies and implies hitting the same date twice or even three times because the first attempt was incorrect. You can notice doubling on three of four numbers, including 9, 0, and/or 4.
